{"tid":387390,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"眼鏡撚入 又比EGG撚","createTime":"2017-09-04T14:55:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T14:55:41.000Z","uid":136989,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1b70c0dd84c510f180fd18a85fbbce7b4daef7f1","tid":387390,"uid":136989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T14:55:41.000Z","msg":"唉 屌 <br />\n買左冇半個月收左皮 <br />\n睇睇下書突然甩左塊鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來眼鏡個圈斷開左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後去到鋪頭話我自己整爛 人為損耗<br />\n同我講個架身幼 唔小心用係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又話佢地公司個貨品部唔會claim比我 <br />\n話公司講過依啲情況唔包 <br />\n咁之後去我相熟間眼鏡鋪 佢同我講架幼係要小心用 但佢話架太幼料差易爛 <br />\n又同我講隻鏡太大 &quot;逼&quot; 爆左隻鏡<br />\n真係冇下次 依間垃圾公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但都好多謝佢地既sales 好好態度 真係想幫我 <br />\n係間公司閪 claim唔到比我 啲貨易爛就咪賣啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nsorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}